```{r pancreas 32402696, include=FALSE}

PMID_32402696 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32402696', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32402696 <- paste0(PMID_32402696$journal,' ', PMID_32402696$year, ' ', PMID_32402696$month,';', PMID_32402696$volume,'(', PMID_32402696$number,'):', PMID_32402696$pages)

PubMed_32402696 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32402696$eprint)

doi_32402696 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32402696$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
